>Hydras:
> 
>Hydras looked amused the escene and say "Wait for now, 
>Rodimus; We always have time to deal with them, by now we have to 
>listen and play wisely " and lookign to Svourge and Cyclonus said "Arent 
>you part of the minions Cyclounus? have you betrayed your master or your master 
>betrayed you? what means that swich of faction?"

Rodimus only continued to chuckle evilly as he stared down Scourge and the disintegration cannon that was aimed at him. 

Slowly, and apparently unwillingly Scourge lowered his weapon, "We have something to settle boy." Scourge said in low threatening tones, "but not here."

Cyclonus nodded and looked back at Hydras, "You know that we had left the services of Unicron from the last time we spoke. I have come to see if you had thought about what we talked about." Cyclonus' optics harden slightly, "You bear the spark of Glavatron and Megatron within you. You have the power to bring together both the Predacons and Decepticons."

Cyclonus' hands clench as he gestures at the other Predacons standing around, "You sit with forces and power at your command, and I have come to remind you of your former greatness! I would join myself with the spark of Galvatron so that he may live again, so that the empire of the decepticons may live again, grow and thrive as it once did."

Cyclonus looked fully again at Hydras, "I have come to see if that is still possible from within you, I have come looking for hope."

OOC: airly, please look at messages #69260 - #69273 under the thread "A spark of hope" to see at least some of the older conversation between Cyclonus and Hydras
